Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.06,Thinking,,0,0,0,,In the fourth year of Emperor Xiàn's reign of Jiàn'ān,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:33.06,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,200 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.40,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè of Eastern Wú died,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:39.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and his younger brother, Sūn Quán, succeeded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.34,0:00:43.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He improved relations with Cáo Cāo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:49.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,and rejected Yuán Shào's \Nproposal for an Anti-Cao front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.56,Thinking,,0,0,0,,That August of the next year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.56,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,August 201 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.66,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yuan Shao raised a force of\N 700,000 to attack Cáo Cāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.20,0:01:12.16,Thinking,,0,0,0,,This was the historically famous battle of Guāndù.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sun Quan may reject my offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.95,0:01:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but what can he do to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With such a mighty host like this, \Nwho in the world could resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Report! Sir, Cáo Cāo has \Nraised 7,000 men in response.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He has camped at Guāndù, and\N already sent his vanguard towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Āhmán truly overestimates himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With only 70,000 petty men, he stands to \Ndefeat our mighty army of 700,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he not striking a stone with only an egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the three armies hasten their march!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will finish this in one battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}My lord, you cannot be so impetuous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}My army is powerful! Why are you talking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}My lord, we are more numerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}but our morale cannot match theirs! They hold that advantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.41,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}but they have few supplies compared to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}We should remain here with our abundant supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.66,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}If we just wait, they will disperse without even a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.24,0:02:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Should we charge forth? That is what Cáo Cāo wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you need to reconsider this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tián Fēng has already hurt our morale and is to be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our mighty army is about to march, and you \Nwish to replicate him?! This is most frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail to take frank advice, \Nyou will be at a disadvantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Men, take him away, and behead this disturber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,180,1540,1900)\pos(495.33,293.444)}Jǔ Shòu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:32.66,That one frame,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,180,1540,1900)\pos(468.63,365.889)}沮授
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Order the three armies out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail to take frank advice, \Nyou will lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, stop this! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To kill our own before a battle will damage our morale!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead imprison him for now, and pass judgment later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, please heed General Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pass judgement after we've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Put Ju Shou away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,After I defeat Cáo Cāo, I'll sentence him and Tian Feng together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.20,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, if you fail to take frank advice, \Nyou will be at a disadvantage! My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All forces, accelerate your advance! Divide the 700,000 force
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,into the east and west camps to block off the enemy troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, please listen or all will be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, if you fail to listen, you will lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire, if you fail to listen, you will lose!
