Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:48.20,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(567,337)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2220)}Guō Jiā\NStyled: Fèngxiào
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, why are you still watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Yuan Shao came eagerly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}and was supposed to go on the offensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}but he's using shields as the front-line now. \NHis intention is to defend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Yuan Shao is able to defend, but you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Our men are elite, equal to ten of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}We must defeat them and shatter their morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}If we stall, our supplies will run out, and the worst will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, if you are to use your force of 70,000 to withstand a force of 700,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}you must act decisively. The slightest hesitation will unnerve our army!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Yuan Shao, before the Emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I petitioned for you to be a Generalissimo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}so why are you rebelling now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}You claim Chancellorship, yet act in treachery!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}It would be a sin not to rebel against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I am under Imperial order to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}And I have {\i1}Their{\i0}  blessing to destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound the drums!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Exterminate the traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Cáo Cāo has fallen back to his camp in Guāndù.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He fled to Guāndù?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Guāndù is the choke-point to Xǔchāng (Xǔdū).
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo seeks to grab my army's very throat with this move
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop us from advancing to Xǔchāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.30,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Have the three armies to press onward to Guāndù.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Order the troops to harass them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not give Cáo Cāo any breathing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we capture Guāndù, Xǔdū can also be taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I believe we can split 10,000 men to blockade Guāndù.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have your troops siege them, build dirt towers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and then to fire into the camps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we constantly harass them thus, and Cáo Cāo retreats in response,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:43.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(599,330)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2220)}Shěn Pèi \N Styled: Zhèng Nán
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,we can seize this choke-point, and Xǔchāng will be within our grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An excellent strategy. Give his order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All regiments, choose elite troops
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and quickly construct dirt towers to trap Cáo Cāo at Guāndù!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say Cáo Cāo is a great commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'll make sure he is unable to advance or retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.00,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(105,390)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2220)}Xún Yōu \N Styled: Gōng Dá
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat, eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Patrol captain, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Wénruò sent us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(100,395)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2220)}Liú Yè \N Styled: Ziyáng
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}The battle at Guāndù has been a stalemate for over a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Though both sides have wins and losses,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Yuan Shao has more soldiers and provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}If this continues, our army will eventually collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Right now, I've left Xǔdū empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}If Yuan Shao splits some of his troops to attack Xǔdū,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}how then can we resist him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Since we are at a major disadvantage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}What if I were to leave early...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}and prepare my military a proper attack in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have said much, so why do you say nothing, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, I came to suggest the plans for the {\i1}'Thunder Mangonel'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I just didn't want you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I just didn't want you to retreat our armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, think about it. We have 70,000 soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}that managed to resist a force of 700,000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}at Guāndù for over a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, you do not have the advantage, but you were never dislodged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Doesn't this show how paltry Yuan Shao's progress is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have returned from Xǔdū (Xǔchāng), carrying a letter from Xún Yù!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Yuan Shao knows you have held together at Guāndù"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.84,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"and wants to make a last stand"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Sire has to match with less against more,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.38,0:16:13.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"If you cannot do this, weakness will be exploited."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.05,0:16:16.58,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"This moment will decide the fate of all."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.28,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Though (Yuan) Shao's army is grand, he can't use it."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"With your divine-like stratagem, what is there to concern?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.72,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Our army may be small, but the borders are drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:30.46,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Grip tightly on the choke-point so they cannot advance."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:32.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"The tide will begin to turn, changing in haste."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:36.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"To strike at this critical moment is a chance utmost vital."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"The borders are drawn"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Grip tightly on the choke-point so they cannot advance"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Tide will begin to turn and disarray will happen..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.84,0:16:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"To strike at this critical moment is a chance utmost vital."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Indeed, we have no time to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, what did sir Xun Yu write for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortify Guāndù.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Grip tightly on the choke-point so they cannot advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But with the conditions before us...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have already reached an impasse at Guāndù for several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,As was said, "the tide will begin to turn".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we persevere, and seize every available opportunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,then it is just as sir Xun Yu summarized, there will be "changing in haste."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.46,0:17:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, the critical task is to stabilize the military and raise our morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, Zǐyáng had just provided us with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Zǐyáng?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:02.42,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,"Thunder Mangonel Schematic"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your back to it, let that bastard taste some steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's two-three hundred feet away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2220)\pos(573.98,405)}Lǐ Diǎn \NStyled: Mànchéng
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.47,0:20:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.41,0:20:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We invited ourselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you two covered in dirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, we managed to spot the enemy digging a hole behind the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}They couldn't beat us openly,\N and so now they try with stealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}The hole was a tunnel dug to sneak in our camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Fear not, for Master Liú Yè ordered the camp to surround the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}This had the enemy waste their resources on the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Chancellor, our provisions are about to run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about to write to Wenruo about this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Have him quickly amass grain and transport it here overnight to relieve the troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, General Xú Huǎng wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngmíng, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor, my subordinate, Shǐ Huàn, went on patrol, and captured a spy for the Yuan army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:21:59.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(117,362)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1900,2220)}Xú Huǎng\NStyled: Gōngmíng
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.59,0:22:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After interrogation, we found out Yuan Shao ordered General Hán Měng to deliver food.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Han Meng is but a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If we send out a few thousand\N light cavalry and intercept him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll sever their supply line and disrupt their army.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Gōngmíng, you can lead your personal forces out first,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll order Zhāng Liáo and Xǔ Chǔ to reinforce you shortly after.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you seize Yuan Shao's food, if he orders soldiers to rescue it,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.02,0:22:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,put your troops in two spots, \Nand crush him in a pincer attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will prepare immediately! I take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.98,0:23:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! We must arrive at the main camp before daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.32,0:24:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the officer before us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just Generals Zhāng and Gāo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.19,0:24:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd arrived just a bit earlier, \Nhow could the food have been seized?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for the seizure of the food and the report of the defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.68,0:24:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,how could our lord have us rescue you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.62,0:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, now quiet! While Xu Huang is still close by, let's kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.07,0:24:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,General, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.34,0:24:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You two, stabilize the formation! I'll meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.62,0:24:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! We've been surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.65,0:25:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You had your supplies seized,\N yet you still have no shame to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.15,0:25:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Men!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.64,0:25:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.28,0:25:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him, and behead him!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.84,0:25:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.52,0:25:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.59,0:25:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.89,0:25:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, our supplies was just seized, so our morale is shaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.80,0:25:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't killing our own officer worsen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.63,0:25:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, General Han has fought fiercely for us before,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.88,0:25:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Cáo Cāo's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.61,0:25:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare him, and let him redeem himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.66,0:25:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, my lord, spare him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.70,0:26:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show mercy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.30,0:26:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.46,0:26:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that our supplies have been stolen, \Ndo any of you know how to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.77,0:26:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, all our grain is stored at Wūcháo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.80,0:26:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We must send forces there to prevent any unforeseen events.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.94,0:27:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already planned that out. You'll go to Yèdū to supervise the supply lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.35,0:27:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ensure the supply line is maintained so our armies will not lack grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.40,0:27:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I obey!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.80,0:27:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chúnyú Qióng?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.46,0:27:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.63,0:27:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wūcháo is our main granary, therefore we'll need heavy forces to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.50,0:27:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You will lead the forces towards Wūcháo. Make sure to defend it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.42,0:27:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not fail me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.06,0:27:32.98,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(113,369)\fade(255,0,255,0,350,1540,1900)}Chúnyú Qióng\NStyled: Zhòngjiān
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.30,0:27:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.22,0:27:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.82,0:27:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.42,0:27:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Jǔ Shòu wants to talk to you about an urgent matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.36,0:27:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.72,0:27:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jǔ Shòu says it's a critical military matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.84,0:27:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how critical it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.45,0:28:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sir, you're in shackles and stocks, no longer a strategist by our lord's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.29,0:28:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tell me what happened quickly, and I will reward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.16,0:28:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only a simple soldier. How could I take such a gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.12,0:28:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to listen, I'll just talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.64,0:28:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,General Han Meng was escorting our grain, when he was intercepted en route, and lost the grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.25,0:28:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lord has sent Master Shěn to Yèdū to supervise the supply line.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.82,0:28:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He also sent Chunyu Qiong to defend Wūcháo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.59,0:28:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is wrong? Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:29:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to tell our lord that a calamity is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.19,0:29:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I have something to say, and I hope you let me say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.09,0:29:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing happening today, so I can humor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.34,0:29:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say there's nothing happening? Disaster's about to strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.99,0:29:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, I have followed you for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.99,0:30:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, on the verge of disaster,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.13,0:30:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you to just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.57,0:30:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you've served me for years that you get to see me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.91,0:30:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise quickly and say what's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.52,0:30:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.22,0:30:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.66,0:30:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in matters of war, the supplies are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.76,0:30:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need you to remind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.50,0:30:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But my lord, though it's such a critical matter, you've barely given thought to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.61,0:30:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Han Meng's provisions have been stolen,\Nand Wūcháo is in grave danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.85,0:31:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I already sent Chunyu Qiong to guard it, heavily.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.52,0:31:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, the problem is exactly that!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.56,0:31:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.16,0:31:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Military matters are none of your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.80,0:31:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It is common knowledge to prioritize supplies in war!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.64,0:31:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've dispatched troops to defend it a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.86,0:31:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}My lord, that Chúnyú Qióng loves alcohol like his own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.22,0:31:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}He drinks so much that he has no thoughts and no plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.58,0:31:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}The whole day, he looks haggard!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.00,0:31:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}With such a dolt, the most incompetent among all,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.00,0:31:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}how could you entrust such a great responsibility to him, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.83,0:31:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Men...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.04,0:31:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.50,0:31:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this brazen fool and throw him in prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.10,0:31:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.58,0:31:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Add more shackles to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.90,0:31:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire! Sire
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.76,0:32:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody release him without my explicit orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.06,0:32:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.45,0:32:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I risked death to warn you of an eminent disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.52,0:32:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You must come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.04,0:32:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.74,0:32:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.19,0:32:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.84,0:32:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.42,0:32:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I want his guard put to death! \NHave somebody else replace him!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.81,0:32:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.37,0:32:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that? Where are you taking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.26,0:32:26.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(589,362)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1580,1940)}Xǔ Yōu\NStyled: Zǐyuǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.11,0:32:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,To answer, Master Xǔ,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.58,0:32:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the patrols have captured this suspicious person just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.38,0:32:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He claims to be a merchant,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.45,0:32:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've found a secret letter from Cáo Cāo to Xǔchāng on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.56,0:32:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're taking him to the main camp to report to our lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.82,0:32:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.32,0:32:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the letter? Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.73,0:32:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a military matter will be reported by me to our lord personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.51,0:33:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In this battle, we must obliterate Cáo Cāo at Guāndù.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.34,0:33:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.35,0:33:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord! My lord! Great news, such great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.95,0:33:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What great news would have you, sir, so elated?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.72,0:33:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indeed great news! \NWe'll destroy Cáo Cāo in one battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mister Xu, tell me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.07,0:33:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, we take our leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.68,0:33:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.35,0:33:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Xu, please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.20,0:33:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}My lord, Cáo Cāo has maintained his army at Guāndù to oppose us for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.94,0:33:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}With this, Xǔchāng is unguarded!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.94,0:33:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}If we divide our army to raid Xǔchāng at night,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.90,0:33:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}then Xǔchāng can be captured, and Cáo Cāo can, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.62,0:34:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Master Xu, how do you know they are running out of supplies?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.52,0:34:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}A patrol captured one of his spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.82,0:34:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}This is a letter from Cáo Cāo to Xǔchāng, urging for supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.10,0:34:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.71,0:34:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo is full of dastardly schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.51,0:34:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this letter is a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.11,0:34:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.62,0:34:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if we do not take Xǔchāng right now, \Nit will harm us in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.22,0:34:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,While Cáo Cāo is indeed devious, this letter cannot be discredited.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.99,0:35:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, you cannot waste this opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.86,0:35:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear my life on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.77,0:35:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be sure that this isn't one of Cáo Cāo's tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.21,0:35:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Xu, how do you know\N Cáo Cāo's thoughts in such a way?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.85,0:35:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.92,0:35:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.25,0:35:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In important matters, how could I dare fool around?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.42,0:35:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo's letter was very clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.23,0:35:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With his supplies running low, his army's about to collapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.83,0:35:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Guāndù can no longer be maintained. How could this be false?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.42,0:35:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.20,0:35:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, Master Shen Pei has a letter for you from Yè Commandery.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.17,0:35:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.80,0:35:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.72,0:35:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"As ordered, I have supervised the provisions for the Yè army in Háncāo."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.50,0:35:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"They are prepared and will arrive soon, assuaging your worries."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"My lord, there is another issue. When Xǔ Yōu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.02,0:35:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Continue
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.19,0:36:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.94,0:36:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"When Xǔ Yōu served in Jì Province,\N he plundered people's property."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.18,0:36:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Furthermore, he had his nephews embezzle taxes and food."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.90,0:36:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}"Thus, I already arrested them."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.16,0:36:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My lord, these are Shen Pei's libels. \NMy lord, do not trust his words at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.16,0:36:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}You are one devious idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.26,0:36:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}How could you face yourself \Nafter presenting your plan to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.70,0:36:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}I'm well aware that you and Cáo Cāo are old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Is it not that you were bribed by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.66,0:36:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}You tried to deceive me in dividing my troops to get me defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.83,0:36:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.07,0:36:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister Xu, what is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.81,0:36:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shen Pei is slandering me! Shen Pei is slandering me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.61,0:36:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have beheaded you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.98,0:37:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I have the authority to do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.40,0:37:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Guards?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.22,0:37:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.55,0:37:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Drag him out! Drag him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.18,0:37:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.75,0:37:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot let him see me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.39,0:37:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.86,0:37:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shen Pei is slandering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.23,0:37:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shen Pei is slandering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.20,0:37:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shen Pei is slandering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.84,0:37:35.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Getting offended over honest advice, these petty men don't deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.28,0:37:38.80,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Yuan Shao refuses to accept loyal words, for that Cáo Cāo will defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.49,0:37:41.49,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Then why not surrender to Cáo Cāo?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.44,0:38:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn animals, there's not enough for us yet you waste all your food.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.10,0:38:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't our lord's horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.91,0:38:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.44,0:38:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please report to the Chancellor. The patrols found this gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.42,0:38:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He says he needs to talk with the Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.40,0:38:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chancellor was busy all night planning with his generals.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.92,0:38:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He just went to sleep. Report to him after he wakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.16,0:38:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This fellow says it's an urgent \Nmatter, and it can't be delayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.09,0:38:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I stutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.30,0:38:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chancellor is asleep. Who'd dare awaken him?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.87,0:39:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mengde!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.85,0:39:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mengde!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.00,0:39:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's shouting!?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.41,0:39:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Xǔ Yōu of Nányáng has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.52,0:39:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.54,0:39:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}Sir, you are the Chancellor while I am commoner. You don't have to be polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.77,0:39:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! Come, come, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.20,0:39:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(353.001,443)}We're just friends, so why mention our ranks?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.16,0:39:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Come! Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.31,0:39:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.95,0:39:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After you!
